WEBVTT

00:10.443 --> 00:11.910
I told them you were awake.

00:11.978 --> 00:14.572
Happy birthday, Geoffrey!

00:15.949 --> 00:17.974
I'm so touched.

00:18.051 --> 00:19.678
May I get you anything?

00:20.587 --> 00:21.747
Don't be silly.

00:21.821 --> 00:25.587
You're always worried about pleasing us,
but today it's Saturday, we're home...

00:25.658 --> 00:27.626
and we're waiting on you.

00:28.294 --> 00:30.057
This is highly irregular.

00:30.130 --> 00:31.825
I don't want to hear it.

00:31.998 --> 00:33.693
Today, we're your butlers.

00:34.501 --> 00:36.401
Here's breakfast in bed.

00:37.003 --> 00:39.301
Is there anything else you would like?

00:39.372 --> 00:40.862
A spot of tea.

00:45.345 --> 00:47.575
I'll get the tea.

00:47.647 --> 00:49.137
Would you like anything with that?

00:49.215 --> 00:51.706
Geoffrey, relax. It's your birthday.

00:51.785 --> 00:54.083
We're gonna do
all of your most hated chores.

00:54.154 --> 00:56.679
But, sir, I don't hate any of my chores.

00:56.756 --> 00:58.155
We do.

00:59.025 --> 01:01.960
Are you going to do
anything special for your birthday?

01:02.028 --> 01:03.757
Most assuredly, Miss Ashley.

01:03.830 --> 01:08.790
<i>Tonight, I'll be enjoying a BBC broadcast
of Gilbert and Sullivan's HMS Pinafore...</i>

01:09.002 --> 01:11.971
followed by a penetrating interview
by David Frost.

01:13.840 --> 01:15.933
And they say the man can't party.

01:17.577 --> 01:19.442
Before we get you your tea...

01:19.512 --> 01:22.003
there's something else
we'd like to do for you.

01:23.616 --> 01:26.346
Carlton, put away
that tired old kazoo, please.

01:27.921 --> 01:29.980
Get busy for me one time, Skinny A.

01:30.056 --> 01:31.921
"Happy birthday, my man G

01:31.991 --> 01:34.016
"Because you know the most
About butlery

01:34.094 --> 01:36.289
"So don't move an inch, stay where you sit

01:36.362 --> 01:38.922
"We're going to treat you like
The King of Brit"

